Peter Treadway, author of "Investing
in The Age of Sovereign Defaults: How to Preserve Your Wealth in
The Coming Crisis", discusses Japan's economic policy. Treadway 
talked with Bloomberg's Pimm Fox and  Carol Massar  on Bloomberg 
